{"tid":410041,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"★缺堤了！iOS 11 頻傳災情 網友哀號","createTime":"2017-09-22T14:33:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-05T05:22:50.000Z","uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"41b77f66f79869853209d46f1a882f9cdf12910f","tid":410041,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T14:33:01.000Z","msg":"iOS 11 號稱 iOS 史上最大躍進，在測試版本中推出破紀錄的 10 個測試版本才在 20 日正式推出，許多使用者也已提早更新了，但現在你可能會想要再等等，因為目前來看&hellip;&hellip;災情似乎有些慘重。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>iOS 11 速度變慢？</strong> <br />\n<br />\n許多網友在更新完後，紛紛上網表示手機速度變慢，尤其以 iPhone 6 用戶的反應最「熱烈」。雖然這部分反應兩極，有些人表示重開機以後就比較正常了，也有些人表示卡到不行！另外也有人表示升級完後手機很容易過熱、比較耗電。也有人說完全沒遇到這些問題？（所以看起來是人品問題？）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.technews.tw/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/21173136/b4aec6220f693a4814d7058d3c342ffb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.technews.tw%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F09%2F21173136%2Fb4aec6220f693a4814d7058d3c342ffb.jpg&h=fa60e5a7&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n以筆者自己 iPhone 6s 在 iOS 11 Beta 測試版開始使用到昨天正式升級的經驗來看，剛升級完以後確實感覺卡卡的，但重開機以後正常點，不過，仍可以感覺在開／關 App 的速度上，iOS 11 的開啟速度似乎比 iOS 10.3.3 要慢一點，一部分是因為過場動畫的速度比前版慢，不過這部分其實可取消過場動畫來解決；另一部分是 App 開啟後的戴入速度也變慢一點點，這部分表現不一定，時快時慢。<br />\n<br />\n根據國外知名 YouTuber Everythingapplepro 的測試，他分別以 iPhone 5s、iPhone 6、iPhone 6s、iPhone SE、iPhone 7、iPhone 7 Plus（iPhone 5 表示哭哭）開機速度、開啟 App 速度、通知列、控制中心等，最後展示 Geekbench 的跑分數據比較，測試版本是 iOS 11 和 iOS 10.3.3。<br />\n<br />\n綜合測試結果下來，越新的手機配合 iOS 11 當然越順就不用多說了，不過 iPhone 5s 有點慘，iOS 11 在各方面的速度測試都比 iOS 10.3.3 還要慢，建議 iPhone 5s 維持 10.3.3 就好了，除非日後蘋果有更新。iPhone 7 比較中，iOS 11 各方面速度都贏過 10.3.3，新手機建議可升級。<br />\n<br />\n以 Geekbench 的數據來看，下圖 iOS 11 的數據在左、iOS 10.3.3 的數據在右；第一排由左至右分別是 iPhone 6s、iPhone 7、iPhone 7 Plus，第二排由左至右分別是 iPhone 5s、iPhone 6、iPhone SE。[/quote]<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.technews.tw/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/21173134/5191c13cc843fa308493716e03ce8db8-e1505986322644.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.technews.tw%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F09%2F21173134%2F5191c13cc843fa308493716e03ce8db8-e1505986322644.jpg&h=86df14dc&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n從圖可看出端倪。整體來看 iOS 11 大致上比舊版本的分數要低一些，不過因為差距不大，如果單就數據來看，實在不能斷言 iOS 11 比 iOS 10.3.3 慢。iOS 11 在單核的分數表現普遍比 iOS 10.3.3 差，多核表現則較好。<br />\n<br />\n另外以安兔兔跑分數據來看，其實也得到和 Geekbench 差不多的結果，但在各手機、各版本 iOS 的表現都不太一樣（手機版本和 iOS 版本擺放位置同 Geekbench 測試）。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.technews.tw/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/21173141/c60c56c2dec80a337640b193fbbfedef.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.technews.tw%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F09%2F21173141%2Fc60c56c2dec80a337640b193fbbfedef.jpg&h=1fa78e25&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<strong>控制中心 Wi-Fi 藍牙關假的？</strong> <br />\n<br />\n相信 iOS 用戶應該很習慣使用控制中心的 Wi-Fi 和藍牙開關快捷鍵吧！但在 iOS 11，國外媒體發現，使用控制中心的 Wi-Fi 快捷鍵關閉，並不代表 Wi-Fi 真正關閉，藍牙也有一樣問題。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.technews.tw/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/21173137/916916043251b363795f8ddb9b6b0bad.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.technews.tw%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F09%2F21173137%2F916916043251b363795f8ddb9b6b0bad.jpeg&h=ef8333c1&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n這問題筆者 20 日更新完也有碰到，明明已經在控制中心把 Wi-Fi 關閉，結果去一趟便利商店回來發現 Wi-Fi 已連結&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n現在如果想要「確實」關閉 Wi-Fi 和藍牙，iOS 11 用戶只能使用「Old School」法了：乖乖從設定進入兩者個別設定，並從設定裡手動關閉。[/quote]<br />\n<a href=\"https://technews.tw/2017/09/22/ios-11-outgoing-caused-severe-users-lament-slow-wi-fi-blue-teeth-but-no-control-center-did-shut-down/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftechnews.tw%2F2017%2F09%2F22%2Fios-11-outgoing-caused-severe-users-lament-slow-wi-fi-blue-teeth-but-no-control-center-did-shut-down%2F&d=xPvb5zCE1hvAv7d1YEpdmP9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=95424055\" target=\"_blank\">https://technews.tw/2017/09/22/ios-11-outgoing-caused-severe-users-lament-slow-wi-fi-blue-teeth-but-no-control-center-did-shut-down/</a>"},{"pid":"41f9d142d99d9bb2f3ce970f97dcc29a1f8e0a87","tid":410041,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T14:33:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bcb4f6e61cdb2614bdb86b546c37440078e50b0","tid":410041,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T14:34:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">因為目前來看&hellip;&hellip;災情似乎有些慘重。<br />\n因為目前來看&hellip;&hellip;災情似乎有些慘重。<br />\n因為目前來看&hellip;&hellip;災情似乎有些慘重。<br />\n因為目前來看&hellip;&hellip;災情似乎有些慘重。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c8879872c2b7f1e51e022065f6aeb0491f2011c","tid":410041,"uid":52215,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T14:34:46.000Z","msg":"唔係話iphone用四年都好順架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16421052c2f6b752ffc1959cb9954c9bc7dc2ef1","tid":410041,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T14:35:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">因為目前來看&hellip;&hellip;災情似乎有些慘重。<br />\n因為目前來看&hellip;&hellip;災情似乎有些慘重。<br />\n因為目前來看&hellip;&hellip;災情似乎有些慘重。<br />\n因為目前來看&hellip;&hellip;災情似乎有些慘重。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc4269b11558952a6af01f1542ed3ad5cd0d4e01","tid":410041,"uid":609,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T14:38:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔係話iphone用四年都好順架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n因住班ifan入黎咬你！<br />\n<br />\n佢地個個都話部5s仲好順架<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9be25a4662c7ae332c42a3a0af639ff03ba2a85","tid":410041,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T14:39:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔係話iphone用四年都好順架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n維持原生ios 係"},{"pid":"acb8453c2bd1db65677c6c83564154bb80204366","tid":410041,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T14:39:57.000Z","msg":"老貓好落力 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65d0821c0cd2dca4ed51dbf1839d20d389d7087e","tid":410041,"uid":73054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T14:44:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔係話iphone用四年都好順架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n比個基佬屌足四年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7c846b0014f9c2fa5b1b36bb42f555975d924ad","tid":410041,"uid":30837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T14:47:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔係話iphone用四年都好順架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n維持原生ios 係</blockquote><br />\n唔update其實係真係好順"},{"pid":"1b6c4d22b00aca1af02467494246958e6b85a555","tid":410041,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T14:53:18.000Z","msg":"iOS 11新照片格式HEVC 無法讓Windows直接讀取 用戶頭痛 !!!<br />\n<br />\n針對iOS 11，蘋果特地導入HEVC(High Efficiency Video Coding)高效率視訊編碼(亦稱為 H.265)技術，以及HEIF(High Efficiency Image File Format)高效率圖檔格式，能進一步降低相機所拍攝的影片、照片在iOS裝置中所占據的空間，替小容量iPhone用戶再添福音。但是，這項嶄新的功能並不是所有作業系統或者雲端服務都有支持，初期使用上可能會對Windows使用者帶來一些困擾。<br />\n<br />\n將iOS 11所拍攝的照片(HEIC格式)分享到其他比較小型的網站上時(例如，編輯利用Pushbullet App將iPhone所拍的照片上傳雲端，再下載到Windows 7的電腦中)，就<span style=\"color: red;\">無法直接讀取</span>(需要轉檔)，會遭遇出乎意料的使用挑戰。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20170920003230-260412\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinatimes.com%2Frealtimenews%2F20170920003230-260412&d=xPvb5zCE1hvAv7d1YEpdmP9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=54b8f9b5\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20170920003230-260412</a>"},{"pid":"bc151035044db07cc6844a4b0dcb929c3592cb1b","tid":410041,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T15:23:56.000Z","msg":"9.3.5"},{"pid":"5ec80501d6cb6506e50fa37e25c3e24cfdc3c4a0","tid":410041,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T15:30:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6969b2b41902ce79481ecec28c97a273334b22da","tid":410041,"uid":7076,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T15:35:32.000Z","msg":"關藍牙同Wi-Fi開關真係勁on9<br />\n點解唔可以design到3D touch 長禁就完全熄咗佢，唔通真係咁困難🤔？"},{"pid":"a3875cebd1e7c069ebe26b928e16784707f1ef17","tid":410041,"uid":35537,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T15:42:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>關藍牙同Wi-Fi開關真係勁on9<br />\n點解唔可以design到3D touch 長禁就完全熄咗佢，唔通真係咁困難🤔？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點解 control centre 既 wifi / BT，唔係按下不是全關？<br />\n<br />\n因為 Apple 當你有整晒 Apple watch / Air pod，如果按下全關就會同其餘 devices 連接中斷，或者會斷晒 home sharing / airdrop / airplay ... 不是很貼心嗎？"},{"pid":"b43e2e8ed8de08859e48358792bd54408dea4e7b","tid":410041,"uid":35537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T15:42:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>關藍牙同Wi-Fi開關真係勁on9<br />\n點解唔可以design到3D touch 長禁就完全熄咗佢，唔通真係咁困難🤔？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點解 control centre 既 wifi / BT，唔係按下不是全關？<br />\n<br />\n因為 Apple 當你有整晒 Apple watch / Air pod，如果按下全關就會同其餘 devices 連接中斷，或者會斷晒 home sharing / airdrop / airplay ... 不是很貼心嗎？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nSorry, the source<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.engadget.com/2017/09/20/ios-11-control-center-doesnt-fully-turn-off-wifi-or-bluetooth/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.engadget.com%2F2017%2F09%2F20%2Fios-11-control-center-doesnt-fully-turn-off-wifi-or-bluetooth%2F&d=xPvb5zCE1hvAv7d1YEpdmP9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=77d71f6d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.engadget.com/2017/09/20/ios-11-control-center-doesnt-fully-turn-off-wifi-or-bluetooth/</a>"},{"pid":"aab174c0706ecf66de1e66941639e90999744483","tid":410041,"uid":4672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T15:58:20.000Z","msg":"下一個topic係咪 ios用家喊爆了 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a859cc1db16e191a31eb77f21579babf19b79168","tid":410041,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T09:08:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfe629ab64d2f2d66950c479877222f95df05b5b","tid":410041,"uid":91398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T09:40:53.000Z","msg":"上下look係有lag<br />\nPad game又有窒嘅感覺<br />\n<br />\n7plus"},{"pid":"9390c85a5aab220b15f16a05012abc219f70d9d0","tid":410041,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T09:46:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/23/174609_c75fc4a295b039bc8caa63d916edb802.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F23%2F174609_c75fc4a295b039bc8caa63d916edb802.jpg&h=7586a488&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n點睇游b唔焗腳了？"},{"pid":"666c9211776149a54ef1d33f7c752b56a807ea7f","tid":410041,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T05:15:41.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"6f71985c158e794b8885d061acff2c876e75bc9d","tid":410041,"uid":22553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T05:22:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>關藍牙同Wi-Fi開關真係勁on9<br />\n點解唔可以design到3D touch 長禁就完全熄咗佢，唔通真係咁困難🤔？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點解 control centre 既 wifi / BT，唔係按下不是全關？<br />\n<br />\n因為 Apple 當你有整晒 Apple watch / Air pod，如果按下全關就會同其餘 devices 連接中斷，或者會斷晒 home sharing / airdrop / airplay ... 不是很貼心嗎？</blockquote><br />\n藍牙/wifi應該開條特別通道，只係開比apple產品連接，唔係依家咁乜鳩都開曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}